		<td><b>Musical symbols for effects in tracker</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I was considering making a tracker for my music engine some time in the future, and I might represent effects with musical symbols instead of letters. Any suggestion for better symbols?<br /><br />If you've never seen open noteheads attached to sixteenth or thirty-second notes before, the symbols for fast and slow arpeggio are inspired by <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tremolo#Notation" class="postlink">tremolo notation</a> as described in <a href="https://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=16517" class="postlink">a recent discussion about slow arps</a>.

		
			<br clear="all" /><br />

