	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Looks pretty good and easy to read to me. The volume symbols - while they make sense to someone who can read scores - aren’t selfexplanatory though. Maybe piecharts could work? ”Full moon” would be 100% and ”empty circle” would be 0%<br /><br />What’s the method of input?

		

